headline: Trump’s Trade War Is Making US Farmers Anxious About Demand Risk
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Josh Yoder, a fifth-generation farmer in Ohio, has been watching gyrations in the crop markets as Donald Trump moved to dramatically escalate his trade war with China this week.
